<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
Not sure if this is a bug or not, but I couldn't find the command to change the melee style for a Bard in CVS 2.3 dated 7/22. I looked in changes.txt and didn't see any mention of moving this command elsewhere. <p>
The command is in the m menu, change melee style, but you need a skill level &gt; 0 in the Weaponmastery skill and e.g. in the Bareand-combat skill. Since the race modifier to combat is implemented as a bonus / malus to the Weaponmastery skill in this version, it could be that your Weaponmastery skill is 0, which does'nt allow you to change the combat style. 
</p>
